Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.08,0:00:05.30,TBHX; Twitter SRC - EN,,0,0,0,,Please, I want you to take this child.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.34,0:00:07.04,TBHX; Twitter SRC - EN,,0,0,0,,Being able to support these children's growth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.29,0:00:09.17,TBHX; Twitter SRC - EN,,0,0,0,,was the reason I opened this orphanage in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.33,0:00:11.12,TBHX; Twitter SRC - EN,,0,0,0,,Woah, you also guessed right this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:12.76,TBHX; Twitter SRC - EN,,0,0,0,,That would be ten in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:13.92,TBHX; Twitter SRC - EN,,0,0,0,,Say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:16.42,TBHX; Twitter SRC - EN,,0,0,0,,Just why are you so lucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:18.51,TBHX; Twitter SRC - EN,,0,0,0,,Behind that disaster
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:20.42,TBHX; Twitter SRC - EN,,0,0,0,,there are too many scandals that have been buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:23.05,TBHX; Twitter SRC - EN,,0,0,0,,Look at each and every one of their genuine smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.75,0:00:25.92,TBHX; Twitter SRC - EN,,0,0,0,,Those are all because of the hope we have given them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:28.26,TBHX; Twitter SRC - EN,,0,0,0,,Why does it have to be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:30.67,TBHX; Twitter SRC - EN,,0,0,0,,I don't really want to be some hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:34.30,TBHX; Twitter SRC - EN,,0,0,0,,I want to be an ordinary person that can make mistakes.
